content: Great augmentation to racing experience with Carrera digital slot car race track. Author keeps improving the app and pays attention to customer feedback. Very happy with the add-ins! Thanks!!

I just picked up SmartRace this evening to start playing around with it as I had heard nothing but good things about it. I have to say, in the short time I used it, I am very happy with how easy it is to use and how well it works.  I do have one minor issue, but I am not sure if it something I am doing or just a glitch in the system a whole. When restarting a race under caution, the race resumes but a split second afterwards the race pauses again as if the track is under caution. This is not the result of a false start either, as I had this happen  with only myself as a driver and a ghost car, and the system does alert you when there is a false start. This issue doesn't happen on every attempt to resume the race, but will happen 2, possibly 3 times during a 50 lap race. It isn't a big concern, as it will resume the race again after hitting "Start" without issue.
If you like the real experience of racing this app is a must-have. If you have Carrera 132 1:24 scale digital slot car set
If you have a Carrera track, you want this

I wish it had the countdown voice like the Carrera app. I'm a brand new user and the app is asking me to rate it a little too soon. Give users more time to use the app before asking to rate it :) EDIT: Change to 5 stars because the developer is totally on top of this app!  EDIT: HUGE UPDATE TO APP!  I submitted several ideas and all but 1 was implemented! This rating system needs more stars! Great Work!
